      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This well-maintained vehicle is in great shape and offers a smooth, reliable ride that you can count on! It has been cared for nicely and shows only the expected minor wear for its age, making it a fantastic value for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks sharp on the road. Come see why this solid performer is the perfect fit for your garage!",
