    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014super dependable and drives like a dream! It\u2019s got a little bit of character from the road, but honestly, it\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more miles. If you're looking for a reliable set of wheels that won't let you down, this is the one. Feel free to give me a shout if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
