      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 generation Carrera features the 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering 320hp with a linear power band optimized by VarioCam Plus technology. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers crisp, precise throws, paired with a rear-wheel-drive configuration for unfiltered mechanical feedback. The vehicle has been proactively maintained with an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and recent ignition coil pack replacements. Its MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry remain tight, providing excellent damping and chassis composure under lateral load. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain is robust, supported by a recent positive compression test and clean bore-scope inspection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
