    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only minor road peppering on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple with minimal bolstering wear, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it has been fastidiously maintained with a documented service history, offering a smooth, responsive drive and quiet idle. It sits on a set of high-quality tires with significant tread life remaining. This is a turn-key car: reliable, aesthetically pleasing, and ready for its next owner to drive away with peace of mind.",
      "price": 34800.0,
